n trung tâm ăn chay, nội soi đại tràng, v.v. Mỗi khi họ mở mắt ra, thế giới thay đổi dựa trên những gì họ nói. Liệu dự án giữ lời hứa của SUPER JUNIOR trong thế giới khó lường và bị chi phối bởi lời nói này có thành công không?</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"287163","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2025-07-26T11:06:17.000Z","cast":["Kim Hee-chul","Shindong","Choi Si-won","Donghae","Cho Kyu-hyun","Leeteuk","Eunhyuk","Yesung","Ryeowook"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Kim Hee-chul","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kim Hee-chul","tmdb_id":1241032,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w521FQ30VXdvjEfj0sZcn1sON5b.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1241032"},{"name":"Shindong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Shindong","tmdb_id":1246965,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n8r2pCE2fqdxCDq4dVJBJJSs757.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1246965"},{"name":"Choi Si-won","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Choi Si-won","tmdb_id":77318,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9NWbnMRKDa6HV2OeoNw0wTeyl6t.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/77318"},{"name":"Donghae","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Donghae","tmdb_id":1246923,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1YrbpTSV4touEQJJwBZW5X6pVLx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1246923"},{"name":"Cho Kyu-hyun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Cho Kyu-hyun","tmdb_id":1246926,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7fcrhuu3fffGT1P1BYf7MfkNt7c.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1246926"},{"name":"Leeteuk","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Leeteuk","tmdb_id":1233717,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aklz9AFWbYu2a2RuF8uKpjNojK6.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1233717"},{"name":"Eunhyuk","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Eunhyuk","tmdb_id":1350129,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1TpPdKRmY5n08NgzHmrRVznKYRT.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1350129"},{"name":"Yesung","nam